<dl id="n41072c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n41" href="#n41072c">N41 (VI.B.33)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n41all.htm#n41072c"> 72(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> <font face="wake">C</font> tells fantastic / love lie</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">The most genuine kind of lying in the world is purely <mark>fantastic lying</mark>, which arises from a desire to escape from the uninteresting actualities of life. <small> Filson Young, <a name="FYTF" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#FYTF"><cite title="source">Trial of Frederick Bywaters and Edith Thompson</cite></a> (1923) xxvi</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
